                                "template": "content",
                                "options": {
                                    "text": "Come meet Santa and other Harker alumni to celebrate the holiday season. We will have cookie decorating, crafts, games, story time, breakfast and, of course, Santa! A professional photographer will be on hand to take family pictures with Santa. 
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        Please RSVP with your name and your children's names and ages. Feel free to invite other alumni families and your friends! 
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        Karri Sakai Baker '84<br>
                                        Director of Alumni Relations<br>
                                        408.345.9264 | <a href=\"mailto:alumni@harker.org\">alumni@harker.org</a>"
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "list",
                                "options": {
                                    "type": "unstyled",
                                    "items": [
                                        "<strong>Who:</strong> All alumni, alumni families and your friends are welcome!",
                                        "<strong>What:</strong> Pictures with Santa, breakfast, bounce house, crafts and more.",
                                        "<strong>Where:</strong> Harker Lower School Gym, 4300 Bucknall Rd. San Jose, CA 95130",
                                        "<strong>When:</strong> Saturday, Dec. 3, 2016, 9â€“11 a.m."
                                    ]
                                }
                            },
                            {   
                                "template": "button",
                                "options": {
                                    "type": "primary", // primary, secondary, outline
                                    "text": "Reply to this Email to RSVP!",
                                    "href": "mailto:alumni@harker.org"
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
